biography: As an aside to the musical works realised by Church of the Cosmic Skull, I have decided to release some other material under my own name, via this new website, billfisher.net Rest assured that the Church has never been stronger, and will continue to spread the light of the Cosmic Rainbow with full and unstoppable force, with new songs and other tantalisations soon to follow. The works to be sent forth from this new platform will be myriad and multiform, varied in genre but of high standard and rich with heart. The first will take the form of a full studio album, an exploration into heavier realms but still very much melody driven; prog with elements of proto-metal and stoner rock. Look out for further developments soonâ€¦ Yours in peace and harmony, Read more on Last.fm. User-contributed text is available under the Creative Commons By-SA License; additional terms may apply.
